+# Flight Plan: Phase 3 — Config + CLI + MCP Surface
+
+**Plan**: [../../cross-file-rels-plan.md](../../cross-file-rels-plan.md)
+**Phase**: Phase 3: Config + CLI + MCP Surface
+**Generated**: 2026-03-13
+**Status**: Landed
